{
  "video_id": "wzkFoetp-_M",
  "title": "What it's like to be a Muslim in America | Dalia Mogahed",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13150.0,
      "end_time": 15390.0,
      "text": "What do you think when you look at me?"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16000.0,
      "end_time": 18500.0,
      "text": "A woman of faith? An expert?"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19145.0,
      "end_time": 20674.0,
      "text": "Maybe even a sister."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21391.0,
      "end_time": 23677.0,
      "text": "Or oppressed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 23702.0,
      "end_time": 25213.0,
      "text": "brainwashed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 25237.0,
      "end_time": 26625.0,
      "text": "a terrorist."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 28610.0,
      "end_time": 31607.0,
      "text": "Or just an airport security line delay."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 32570.0,
      "end_time": 34800.0,
      "text": "That one&#39;s actually true."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 34104.0,
      "end_time": 35660.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 35684.0,
      "end_time": 38907.0,
      "text": "If some of your perceptions were negative, I don&#39;t really blame you."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 38931.0,
      "end_time": 41500.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s just how the media has been portraying"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 41750.0,
      "end_time": 42605.0,
      "text": "people who look like me."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 42629.0,
      "end_time": 44350.0,
      "text": "One study found"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 44590.0,
      "end_time": 48803.0,
      "text": "that 80 percent of news coverage about Islam and Muslims is negative."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 48828.0,
      "end_time": 53640.0,
      "text": "And studies show that Americans say that most don&#39;t know a Muslim."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 53880.0,
      "end_time": 55944.0,
      "text": "I guess people don&#39;t talk to their Uber drivers."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 55968.0,
      "end_time": 57886.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 59365.0,
      "end_time": 62964.0,
      "text": "Well, for those of you who have never met a Muslim,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 62988.0,
      "end_time": 64833.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s great to meet you."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 65738.0,
      "end_time": 67688.0,
      "text": "Let me tell you who I am."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 68731.0,
      "end_time": 71833.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m a mom, a coffee lover --"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 71858.0,
      "end_time": 73686.0,
      "text": "double espresso, cream on the side."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 74103.0,
      "end_time": 75442.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m an introvert."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 76890.0,
      "end_time": 78960.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m a wannabe fitness fanatic."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 78120.0,
      "end_time": 82462.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;m a practicing, spiritual Muslim."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 83788.0,
      "end_time": 88137.0,
      "text": "But not like Lady Gaga says, because baby, I wasn&#39;t born this way."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 88931.0,
      "end_time": 90487.0,
      "text": "It was a choice."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 91640.0,
      "end_time": 94985.0,
      "text": "When I was 17, I decided to come out."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 95679.0,
      "end_time": 98840.0,
      "text": "No, not as a gay person like some of my friends,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 98864.0,
      "end_time": 100364.0,
      "text": "but as a Muslim,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 100388.0,
      "end_time": 103459.0,
      "text": "and decided to start wearing the hijab, my head covering."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 104216.0,
      "end_time": 107235.0,
      "text": "My feminist friends were aghast:"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 107771.0,
      "end_time": 110492.0,
      "text": "\"Why are you oppressing yourself?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 111436.0,
      "end_time": 112968.0,
      "text": "The funny thing was,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 112992.0,
      "end_time": 117960.0,
      "text": "it was actually at that time a feminist declaration of independence"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 118898.0,
      "end_time": 122856.0,
      "text": "from the pressure I felt as a 17-year-old,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 122880.0,
      "end_time": 126526.0,
      "text": "to conform to a perfect and unattainable standard of beauty."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 127582.0,
      "end_time": 132103.0,
      "text": "I didn&#39;t just passively accept the faith of my parents."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 132658.0,
      "end_time": 134863.0,
      "text": "I wrestled with the Quran."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 134888.0,
      "end_time": 139816.0,
      "text": "I read and reflected and questioned and doubted"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 140428.0,
      "end_time": 142490.0,
      "text": "and, ultimately, believed."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 143621.0,
      "end_time": 147868.0,
      "text": "My relationship with God -- it was not love at first sight."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 149614.0,
      "end_time": 152488.0,
      "text": "It was a trust and a slow surrender"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 152512.0,
      "end_time": 155525.0,
      "text": "that deepened with every reading of the Quran."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 156133.0,
      "end_time": 159935.0,
      "text": "Its rhythmic beauty sometimes moves me to tears."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 160909.0,
      "end_time": 164103.0,
      "text": "I see myself in it. I feel that God knows me."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 165690.0,
      "end_time": 170661.0,
      "text": "Have you ever felt like someone sees you, completely understands you"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 170685.0,
      "end_time": 172336.0,
      "text": "and yet loves you anyway?"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 172923.0,
      "end_time": 174553.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s how it feels."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 175773.0,
      "end_time": 178453.0,
      "text": "And so later, I got married,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 178477.0,
      "end_time": 180341.0,
      "text": "and like all good Egyptians,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 180365.0,
      "end_time": 182824.0,
      "text": "started my career as an engineer."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 182848.0,
      "end_time": 184848.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 186602.0,
      "end_time": 190444.0,
      "text": "I later had a child, after getting married,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 191603.0,
      "end_time": 195181.0,
      "text": "and I was living essentially the Egyptian-American dream."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 198448.0,
      "end_time": 202881.0,
      "text": "And then that terrible morning of September, 2001."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 204417.0,
      "end_time": 209363.0,
      "text": "I think a lot of you probably remember exactly where you were that morning."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 211181.0,
      "end_time": 214888.0,
      "text": "I was sitting in my kitchen finishing breakfast,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 214912.0,
      "end_time": 218541.0,
      "text": "and I look up on the screen and see the words \"Breaking News.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 219750.0,
      "end_time": 222465.0,
      "text": "There was smoke, airplanes flying into buildings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 222490.0,
      "end_time": 225253.0,
      "text": "people jumping out of buildings."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 225277.0,
      "end_time": 226940.0,
      "text": "What was this?"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 227456.0,
      "end_time": 228810.0,
      "text": "An accident?"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 229786.0,
      "end_time": 231647.0,
      "text": "A malfunction?"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 233840.0,
      "end_time": 236171.0,
      "text": "My shock quickly turned to outrage."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 236550.0,
      "end_time": 238795.0,
      "text": "Who would do this?"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 239385.0,
      "end_time": 241831.0,
      "text": "And I switch the channel and I hear,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 242111.0,
      "end_time": 243781.0,
      "text": "\"... Muslim terrorist ...,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 244191.0,
      "end_time": 246188.0,
      "text": "\"... in the name of Islam ...,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 246212.0,
      "end_time": 248560.0,
      "text": "\"... Middle-Eastern descent ...,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 248585.0,
      "end_time": 250396.0,
      "text": "\"... jihad ...,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 250420.0,
      "end_time": 251870.0,
      "text": "\"... we should bomb Mecca.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 252294.0,
      "end_time": 253450.0,
      "text": "Oh my God."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 255232.0,
      "end_time": 259550.0,
      "text": "Not only had my country been attacked,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 259790.00000000003,
      "end_time": 260421.00000000003,
      "text": "but in a flash,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 260446.00000000003,
      "end_time": 264352.0,
      "text": "somebody else&#39;s actions had turned me from a citizen"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 264376.0,
      "end_time": 265798.0,
      "text": "to a suspect."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 267210.0,
      "end_time": 271958.0,
      "text": "That same day, we had to drive across Middle America"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 271982.0,
      "end_time": 275389.0,
      "text": "to move to a new city to start grad school."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 276908.0,
      "end_time": 278991.0,
      "text": "And I remember sitting in the passenger seat"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 279150.0,
      "end_time": 280990.0,
      "text": "as we drove in silence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 281871.0,
      "end_time": 284457.0,
      "text": "crouched as low as I could go in my seat,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 284481.0,
      "end_time": 289998.0,
      "text": "for the first time in my life, afraid for anyone to know I was a Muslim."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 290943.0,
      "end_time": 294850.0,
      "text": "We moved into our apartment that night in a new town"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 294110.0,
      "end_time": 296879.0,
      "text": "in what felt like a completely different world."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 297928.0,
      "end_time": 301882.0,
      "text": "And then I was hearing and seeing and reading"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 301906.0,
      "end_time": 304603.0,
      "text": "warnings from national Muslim organizations"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 304627.0,
      "end_time": 307558.0,
      "text": "saying things like, \"Be alert,\" \"Be aware,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 308312.0,
      "end_time": 311428.0,
      "text": "\"Stay in well-lit areas,\" \"Don&#39;t congregate.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 312180.0,
      "end_time": 314710.0,
      "text": "I stayed inside all week."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 314988.0,
      "end_time": 317732.0,
      "text": "And then it was Friday that same week,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 317756.0,
      "end_time": 321152.0,
      "text": "the day that Muslims congregate for worship."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 322350.0,
      "end_time": 326601.0,
      "text": "And again the warnings were, \"Don&#39;t go that first Friday,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 326625.0,
      "end_time": 328347.0,
      "text": "it could be a target.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 329512.0,
      "end_time": 332163.0,
      "text": "And I was watching the news, wall-to-wall coverage."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 332187.0,
      "end_time": 335520.0,
      "text": "Emotions were so raw, understandably,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 335760.0,
      "end_time": 338194.0,
      "text": "and I was also hearing about attacks on Muslims,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 338778.0,
      "end_time": 341596.0,
      "text": "or people who were perceived to be Muslim, being pulled out"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 341620.0,
      "end_time": 342842.0,
      "text": "and beaten in the street."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 342866.0,
      "end_time": 344979.0,
      "text": "Mosques were actually firebombed."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 345400.0,
      "end_time": 346992.0,
      "text": "And I thought, we should just stay home."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 347777.0,
      "end_time": 350525.0,
      "text": "And yet, something didn&#39;t feel right."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 351335.0,
      "end_time": 353768.0,
      "text": "Because those people who attacked our country"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 353792.0,
      "end_time": 356109.0,
      "text": "attacked our country."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 358611.0,
      "end_time": 361417.0,
      "text": "I get it that people were angry at the terrorists."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 361441.0,
      "end_time": 363561.0,
      "text": "Guess what? So was I."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 364897.0,
      "end_time": 368340.0,
      "text": "And so to have to explain yourself all the time isn&#39;t easy."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 370193.0,
      "end_time": 373730.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t mind questions. I love questions."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 373582.0,
      "end_time": 375771.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s the accusations that are tough."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 376583.0,
      "end_time": 379230.0,
      "text": "Today we hear people actually saying things like,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 380278.0,
      "end_time": 383840.0,
      "text": "\"There&#39;s a problem in this country, and it&#39;s called Muslims."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 383108.0,
      "end_time": 384946.0,
      "text": "When are we going to get rid of them?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 385504.0,
      "end_time": 388716.0,
      "text": "So, some people want to ban Muslims and close down mosques."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 389197.0,
      "end_time": 392255.0,
      "text": "They talk about my community kind of like we&#39;re a tumor"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 392279.0,
      "end_time": 393920.0,
      "text": "in the body of America."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 393944.0,
      "end_time": 397205.0,
      "text": "And the only question is, are we malignant or benign?"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 397866.0,
      "end_time": 400847.0,
      "text": "You know, a malignant tumor you extract altogether,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 400871.0,
      "end_time": 406480.0,
      "text": "and a benign tumor you just keep under surveillance."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 407467.0,
      "end_time": 411332.0,
      "text": "The choices don&#39;t make sense, because it&#39;s the wrong question."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 411893.0,
      "end_time": 415794.0,
      "text": "Muslims, like all other Americans, aren&#39;t a tumor in the body of America,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 415818.0,
      "end_time": 417293.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re a vital organ."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 418109.0,
      "end_time": 419109.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 419134.0,
      "end_time": 420293.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 420317.0,
      "end_time": 423537.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 425937.0,
      "end_time": 428503.0,
      "text": "Muslims are inventors and teachers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 428527.0,
      "end_time": 431565.0,
      "text": "first responders and Olympic athletes."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 432341.0,
      "end_time": 435741.0,
      "text": "Now, is closing down mosques going to make America safer?"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 436194.0,
      "end_time": 439270.0,
      "text": "It might free up some parking spots,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 439294.0,
      "end_time": 440936.0,
      "text": "but it will not end terrorism."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 442134.0,
      "end_time": 444587.0,
      "text": "Going to a mosque regularly is actually linked"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 444611.0,
      "end_time": 448517.0,
      "text": "to having more tolerant views of people of other faiths"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 448541.0,
      "end_time": 450563.0,
      "text": "and greater civic engagement."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 451561.0,
      "end_time": 454842.0,
      "text": "And as one police chief in the Washington, DC area"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 454866.0,
      "end_time": 456170.0,
      "text": "recently told me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 456410.0,
      "end_time": 458901.0,
      "text": "people don&#39;t actually get radicalized at mosques."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 458925.0,
      "end_time": 463170.0,
      "text": "They get radicalized in their basement or bedroom, in front of a computer."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 464526.0,
      "end_time": 467356.0,
      "text": "And what you find about the radicalization process"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 467380.0,
      "end_time": 469300.0,
      "text": "is it starts online,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 469270.0,
      "end_time": 470598.0,
      "text": "but the first thing that happens"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 470622.0,
      "end_time": 473616.0,
      "text": "is the person gets cut off from their community,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 473640.0,
      "end_time": 475282.0,
      "text": "from even their family,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 475306.0,
      "end_time": 478730.0,
      "text": "so that the extremist group can brainwash them"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 478980.0,
      "end_time": 482396.0,
      "text": "into believing that they, the terrorists, are the true Muslims,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 482420.0,
      "end_time": 486436.0,
      "text": "and everyone else who abhors their behavior and ideology"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 486460.0,
      "end_time": 489131.0,
      "text": "are sellouts or apostates."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 489607.0,
      "end_time": 491862.0,
      "text": "So if we want to prevent radicalization,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 491886.0,
      "end_time": 495284.0,
      "text": "we have to keep people going to the mosque."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 496765.0,
      "end_time": 500493.0,
      "text": "Now, some will still argue Islam is a violent religion."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 500517.0,
      "end_time": 505466.0,
      "text": "After all, a group like ISIS bases its brutality on the Quran."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 506318.0,
      "end_time": 509652.0,
      "text": "Now, as a Muslim, as a mother, as a human being,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 509676.0,
      "end_time": 514396.0,
      "text": "I think we need to do everything we can to stop a group like ISIS."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 515720.0,
      "end_time": 520600.0,
      "text": "But we would be giving in to their narrative"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 520624.0,
      "end_time": 525756.0,
      "text": "if we cast them as representatives of a faith of 1.6 billion people."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 526373.0,
      "end_time": 529866.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 529890.0,
      "end_time": 531326.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 533809.0,
      "end_time": 537930.0,
      "text": "ISIS has as much to do with Islam"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 537117.0,
      "end_time": 540168.0,
      "text": "as the Ku Klux Klan has to do with Christianity."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 540491.0,
      "end_time": 545158.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 546795.0,
      "end_time": 551830.0,
      "text": "Both groups claim to base their ideology on their holy book."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 552349.0,
      "end_time": 555373.0,
      "text": "But when you look at them, they&#39;re not motivated"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 555397.0,
      "end_time": 557681.0,
      "text": "by what they read in their holy book."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 557705.0,
      "end_time": 562852.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s their brutality that makes them read these things into the scripture."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 564980.0,
      "end_time": 567747.0,
      "text": "Recently, a prominent imam told me a story that really took me aback."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 567772.0,
      "end_time": 569511.0,
      "text": "He said that a girl came to him"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 569535.0,
      "end_time": 571924.0,
      "text": "because she was thinking of going to join ISIS."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 572556.0,
      "end_time": 574604.0,
      "text": "And I was really surprised and asked him,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 574628.0,
      "end_time": 577874.0,
      "text": "had she been in contact with a radical religious leader?"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 577898.0,
      "end_time": 580193.0,
      "text": "And he said the problem was quite the opposite,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 580217.0,
      "end_time": 583944.0,
      "text": "that every cleric that she had talked to had shut her down"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 583968.0,
      "end_time": 587564.0,
      "text": "and said that her rage, her sense of injustice in the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 587589.0,
      "end_time": 589674.0,
      "text": "was just going to get her in trouble."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 589698.0,
      "end_time": 593379.0,
      "text": "And so with nowhere to channel and make sense of this anger,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 593403.0,
      "end_time": 595418.0,
      "text": "she was a prime target to be exploited"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 595442.0,
      "end_time": 598910.0,
      "text": "by extremists promising her a solution."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 598605.0,
      "end_time": 602871.0,
      "text": "What this imam did was to connect her back to God and to her community."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 603319.0,
      "end_time": 608165.0,
      "text": "He didn&#39;t shame her for her rage -- instead, he gave her constructive ways"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 608190.0,
      "end_time": 610727.0,
      "text": "to make real change in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 610751.0,
      "end_time": 615443.0,
      "text": "What she learned at that mosque prevented her from going to join ISIS."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 616983.0,
      "end_time": 618238.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve told you a little bit"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 618262.0,
      "end_time": 621510.0,
      "text": "about how Islamophobia affects me and my family."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 621760.0,
      "end_time": 623616.0,
      "text": "But how does it impact ordinary Americans?"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 623640.0,
      "end_time": 625545.0,
      "text": "How does it impact everyone else?"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 625569.0,
      "end_time": 631334.0,
      "text": "How does consuming fear 24 hours a day affect the health of our democracy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 631359.0,
      "end_time": 633700.0,
      "text": "the health of our free thought?"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 633527.0,
      "end_time": 637398.0,
      "text": "Well, one study -- actually, several studies in neuroscience --"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 637422.0,
      "end_time": 641283.0,
      "text": "show that when we&#39;re afraid, at least three things happen."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 641857.0,
      "end_time": 645978.0,
      "text": "We become more accepting of authoritarianism,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 646200.0,
      "end_time": 648449.0,
      "text": "conformity and prejudice."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 649194.0,
      "end_time": 654981.0,
      "text": "One study showed that when subjects were exposed to news stories"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 655500.0,
      "end_time": 657989.0,
      "text": "that were negative about Muslims,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 658130.0,
      "end_time": 662128.0,
      "text": "they became more accepting of military attacks on Muslim countries"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 662152.0,
      "end_time": 666168.0,
      "text": "and policies that curtail the rights of American Muslims."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 666192.0,
      "end_time": 668349.0,
      "text": "Now, this isn&#39;t just academic."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 668373.0,
      "end_time": 672765.0,
      "text": "When you look at when anti-Muslim sentiment spiked"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 673555.0,
      "end_time": 677103.0,
      "text": "between 2001 and 2013,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 677127.0,
      "end_time": 678694.0,
      "text": "it happened three times,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 678718.0,
      "end_time": 680943.0,
      "text": "but it wasn&#39;t around terrorist attacks."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 681294.0,
      "end_time": 685687.0,
      "text": "It was in the run up to the Iraq War and during two election cycles."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 686155.0,
      "end_time": 690699.0,
      "text": "So Islamophobia isn&#39;t just the natural response to Muslim terrorism"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 690723.0,
      "end_time": 692722.0,
      "text": "as I would have expected."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 693218.0,
      "end_time": 697695.0,
      "text": "It can actually be a tool of public manipulation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 697720.0,
      "end_time": 701703.0,
      "text": "eroding the very foundation of a free society,"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 701727.0,
      "end_time": 705851.0,
      "text": "which is rational and well-informed citizens."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 706605.0,
      "end_time": 709136.0,
      "text": "Muslims are like canaries in the coal mine."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 709655.0,
      "end_time": 711346.0,
      "text": "We might be the first to feel it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 711370.0,
      "end_time": 715407.0,
      "text": "but the toxic air of fear is harming us all."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 716251.0,
      "end_time": 721804.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 723580.0,
      "end_time": 725979.0,
      "text": "And assigning collective guilt"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 726300.0,
      "end_time": 728841.0,
      "text": "isn&#39;t just about having to explain yourself all the time."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 729777.0,
      "end_time": 733425.0,
      "text": "Deah and his wife Yusor were a young married couple"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 733449.0,
      "end_time": 735448.0,
      "text": "living in Chapel Hill, North Carolina,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 735472.0,
      "end_time": 737710.0,
      "text": "where they both went to school."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 737686.0,
      "end_time": 740101.0,
      "text": "Deah was an athlete."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 740125.0,
      "end_time": 743657.0,
      "text": "He was in dental school, talented, promising ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 744260.0,
      "end_time": 748478.0,
      "text": "And his sister would tell me that he was the sweetest,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 748502.0,
      "end_time": 750536.0,
      "text": "most generous human being she knew."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 750561.0,
      "end_time": 754415.0,
      "text": "She was visiting him there and he showed her his resume,"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 754439.0,
      "end_time": 755700.0,
      "text": "and she was amazed."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 755725.0,
      "end_time": 759955.0,
      "text": "She said, \"When did my baby brother become such an accomplished young man?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 761119.0,
      "end_time": 765684.0,
      "text": "Just a few weeks after Suzanne&#39;s visit to her brother and his new wife,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 766237.0,
      "end_time": 767514.0,
      "text": "their neighbor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 768732.0,
      "end_time": 770872.0,
      "text": "Craig Stephen Hicks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 770897.0,
      "end_time": 772642.0,
      "text": "murdered them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 772666.0,
      "end_time": 777447.0,
      "text": "as well as Yusor&#39;s sister, Razan, who was visiting for the afternoon,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 777471.0,
      "end_time": 779230.0,
      "text": "in their apartment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 779754.0,
      "end_time": 781509.0,
      "text": "execution style,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 781533.0,
      "end_time": 785489.0,
      "text": "after posting anti-Muslim statements on his Facebook page."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 786580.0,
      "end_time": 787802.0,
      "text": "He shot Deah eight times."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 789254.0,
      "end_time": 793289.0,
      "text": "So bigotry isn&#39;t just immoral, it can even be lethal."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 794355.0,
      "end_time": 795676.0,
      "text": "So, back to my story."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 795700.0,
      "end_time": 797400.0,
      "text": "What happened after 9/11?"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 797424.0,
      "end_time": 800552.0,
      "text": "Did we go to the mosque or did we play it safe and stay home?"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 801390.0,
      "end_time": 803271.0,
      "text": "Well, we talked it over,"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 803296.0,
      "end_time": 805985.0,
      "text": "and it might seem like a small decision, but to us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 806900.0,
      "end_time": 809865.0,
      "text": "it was about what kind of America we wanted to leave for our kids:"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 809889.0,
      "end_time": 813269.0,
      "text": "one that would control us by fear"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 813293.0,
      "end_time": 816787.0,
      "text": "or one where we were practicing our religion freely."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 816811.0,
      "end_time": 818659.0,
      "text": "So we decided to go to the mosque."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 819823.0,
      "end_time": 821566.0,
      "text": "And we put my son in his car seat,"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 821590.0,
      "end_time": 825281.0,
      "text": "buckled him in, and we drove silently, intensely, to the mosque."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 825305.0,
      "end_time": 829181.0,
      "text": "I took him out, I took off my shoes, I walked into the prayer hall"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 830609.0,
      "end_time": 832179.0,
      "text": "and what I saw made me stop."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 833271.0,
      "end_time": 834899.0,
      "text": "The place was completely full."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 835492.0,
      "end_time": 837680.0,
      "text": "And then the imam made an announcement,"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 837704.0,
      "end_time": 841969.0,
      "text": "thanking and welcoming our guests,"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 842564.0,
      "end_time": 844778.0,
      "text": "because half the congregation"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 845833.0,
      "end_time": 848560.0,
      "text": "were Christians, Jews, Buddhists, atheists,"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 848585.0,
      "end_time": 851500.0,
      "text": "people of faith and no faith,"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 851290.0,
      "end_time": 855930.0,
      "text": "who had come not to attack us, but to stand in solidarity with us."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 856419.0,
      "end_time": 863390.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 865599.0,
      "end_time": 867722.0,
      "text": "I just break down at this time."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 868674.0,
      "end_time": 873218.0,
      "text": "These people were there because they chose courage and compassion"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 873242.0,
      "end_time": 875339.0,
      "text": "over panic and prejudice."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 876731.0,
      "end_time": 878398.0,
      "text": "What will you choose?"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 879122.0,
      "end_time": 884142.0,
      "text": "What will you choose at this time of fear and bigotry?"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 885397.0,
      "end_time": 887108.0,
      "text": "Will you play it safe?"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 887914.0,
      "end_time": 890213.0,
      "text": "Or will you join those who say"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 890237.0,
      "end_time": 892225.0,
      "text": "we are better than that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 892249.0,
      "end_time": 893400.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 893424.0,
      "end_time": 897747.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 907910.0,
      "end_time": 909274.0,
      "text": "Thank you so much."
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 912497.0,
      "end_time": 916841.0,
      "text": "Helen Walters: So Dalia, you seem to have struck a chord."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 916865.0,
      "end_time": 918402.0,
      "text": "But I wonder,"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 918426.0,
      "end_time": 920885.0,
      "text": "what would you say to those who might argue"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 920909.0,
      "end_time": 922665.0,
      "text": "that you&#39;re giving a TED Talk,"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 922690.0,
      "end_time": 924245.0,
      "text": "you&#39;re clearly a deep thinker,"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 924269.0,
      "end_time": 926276.0,
      "text": "you work at a fancy think tank,"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 926300.0,
      "end_time": 928413.0,
      "text": "you&#39;re an exception, you&#39;re not the rule."
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 928437.0,
      "end_time": 930209.0,
      "text": "What would you say to those people?"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 930841.0,
      "end_time": 933763.0,
      "text": "Dalia Mogahed: I would say, don&#39;t let this stage distract you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 933787.0,
      "end_time": 934992.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m completely ordinary."
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 935821.0,
      "end_time": 937660.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m not an exception."
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 937447.0,
      "end_time": 939467.0,
      "text": "My story is not unusual."
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 939491.0,
      "end_time": 942473.0,
      "text": "I am as ordinary as they come."
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 942498.0,
      "end_time": 946696.0,
      "text": "When you look at Muslims around the world --"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 946720.0,
      "end_time": 949551.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;ve done this, I&#39;ve done the largest study ever done"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 949575.0,
      "end_time": 951117.0,
      "text": "on Muslims around the world --"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 951141.0,
      "end_time": 952591.0,
      "text": "people want ordinary things."
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 952615.0,
      "end_time": 954440.0,
      "text": "They want prosperity for their family,"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 954464.0,
      "end_time": 955615.0,
      "text": "they want jobs"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 955639.0,
      "end_time": 957245.0,
      "text": "and they want to live in peace."
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 957269.0,
      "end_time": 960315.0,
      "text": "So I am not in any way an exception."
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 960339.0,
      "end_time": 963190.0,
      "text": "When you meet people who seem like an exception to the rule,"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 963214.0,
      "end_time": 965540.0,
      "text": "oftentimes it&#39;s that the rule is broken,"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 966292.0,
      "end_time": 968512.0,
      "text": "not that they&#39;re an exception to it."
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 968536.0,
      "end_time": 970996.0,
      "text": "HW: Thank you so much. Dalia Mogahed."
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 971200.0,
      "end_time": 975694.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}